title: Houdini 4 Pro w32 CBF

All credits to chessgod101, CBF and chess community.

How to install:

2) use Houdini_4_Pro_w32-v1.exe in any chess GUI like Arena, Chesbase or ChessOK Aquarium.
3) enjoy
